1. Gledaću utakmice* večeras. (I will watch matches tonight.)
2. Utakmice* u našoj ligi su uzbudljive. (Matches in our league are exciting.)
3. Utakmice* u fudbalu mogu biti veoma napete. (Football matches can be very tense.)
4. Naš tim igra tri utakmice* ovog vikenda. (Our team plays three matches this weekend.)
5. Utakmice* su odložene zbog loših vremenskih uslova. (Matches are postponed due to bad weather conditions.)
6. Utakmice* su prilika za ljude da se druže i uživaju zajedno. (Matches are an opportunity for people to socialize and enjoy together.)
7. Utakmice* u košarci su mi omiljene. (Basketball matches are my favorite.)
8. Zbog povrede, igrač će propustiti naredne utakmice*. (Due to injury, the player will miss the upcoming matches.)
9. Utakmice* u tenisu su izuzetno zahtevne fizički. (Tennis matches are extremely physically demanding.)
10. Naš tim je pobedio u svim utakmicama* ove sezone. (Our team won all matches this season.)